title: Frank Stephenson Barnes Fellowship Endowment Fund
description: To provide support for Engineering students at CU Boulder in the Department of Electrical, Computer and Energy Engineering or Interdisciplinary Telecommunications Program in honor of Distinguished Professor Frank Stephenson Barnes.
